mpared to the per minute billing with Telkom. The saving is achieved by utilizing the Least Cost Routing, which converts the outgoing \'93landline-to-cell\'94 calls to \'93cell-to cell\'94 calls. See submissions by Du Pont Telecom (Pty) Ltd on page 266 of the record.}}}
